Kalvakuntla Chandrashekar Rao better known and abbreviated as K.C.R., is an Indian politician and the first Chief Minister of Telangana, a new state formed by the division of Andhra Pradesh in 2014. He is the leader and Founder of the Telangana Rashtra Samithi, a regional party in India. Wikipedia
Born: February 17, 1954 (age 64 years), Siddipet, India
Full name: Kalvakuntla Chandrashekar Rao
Spouse: Shobha Rao (m. 1969)
Education: Osmania University
Siblings: K Ranga Rao
Grandchildren: Devanapalli Anil Aaditya, Alekhya Rao, Himanshu Rao, Devanapalli Anil Aarya
